yle=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">千祈唔好捉鬼</span></span><br />\n<br />\n今日捉鬼捉到咁開心<br />\n下次升級嘅時候<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">班真鬼就以捉鬼為理由將我哋啲手足捉上警車</span></span><br />\n<br />\n屌你地班五毛<br />\n幾時話割蓆？<br />\n叫人走就係割蓆？<br />\n今日d PO到11點為止都非常正常<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冇啦啦會有一班人將今日勸前線走既說話扭曲成係割蓆</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">極懷疑開PO屌分化果d先係五毛</span></span>"},{"pid":"11c2e3154b6010818bbed5e298e333fa1a548714","tid":1485453,"uid":41005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:09:48.000Z","msg":"下一批到first aid <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 辛苦記者守尾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3711977b8a7ea914daa8f9b35d9804c19138fd52","tid":1485453,"uid":287778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:09:49.000Z","msg":"咁多位手足辛苦哂！"},{"pid":"09065bcf3abc71a0c36f9fc075d06f7446619b83","tid":1485453,"uid":293801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:10:05.000Z","msg":"感動"},{"pid":"872092123b1ab179536742869bbca7bf3b98df49","tid":1485453,"uid":266546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:10:05.000Z","msg":"Good job!!! 感激！"},{"pid":"895bd0bbe4d53928443d3f378948eff7ee6d39e8","tid":1485453,"uid":78689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:10:12.000Z","msg":"我愛叻叻手足們<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8e9630ca3412b4d0082aad290fe15bb3ce5076d","tid":1485453,"uid":235890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:10:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbe water!"},{"pid":"4012b9878b0391b274a75aed3c2c902327c0a713","tid":1485453,"uid":171880,"like":0,"dislike